summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; providing for the purchase of an easement for a sanitary sewer over certain land in the southeast one-quarter of Section 30, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., King County, Washington, necessary for the Southwest Kenyon Street Trunk connection, and for the expenses of the Engineering Department in connection with such purchase, and making an appropriation from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund.
